sql:
SELECT name, bullet_weight
FROM cartridges
WHERE bullet_type = 'Jacketed Hollow Point';

SELECT username
FROM users
WHERE last_login >= (SELECT MAX(access_date) FROM access_logs);

SELECT AVG(bullet_weight) AS average_bullet_weight
FROM cartridges
WHERE type = 'rifle';

SELECT cartridge_id, AVG(fps) AS average_velocity
FROM ballistic_data
GROUP BY cartridge_id;

external_knowledge:
Firearm types refer to categories like rifle, pistol, or shotgun; 
"have been accessed" means having at least one entry in the access logs. 
"Average cartridge energies" represent the mean energy in foot-pounds for each firearm type.
